<div class="tag">
<a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e8%af%97%e7%bb%8f">诗经</a>
<span>，</span><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e7%94%9f%e6%b4%bb">生活</a>
</div>
